 cysts are lined by tall columnar epithelium, and some of those cells are ciliated.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.049638,0.064897,0.085094,0.10239,0.1088,0.1088,0.10402,0.093365,0.08588,0.084062,0.067125,0.045919],"unified_progress":[0.060683,0.084432,0.069298,0.10279,0.10515,0.10661,0.097212,0.093349,0.084334,0.077434,0.065788,0.052918]},{"section":8,"text":"That's a pretty specific clue!","dimension":0,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.038486,0.10381,0.11499,0.11971,0.11501,0.10918,0.098295,0.082199,0.076085,0.06233,0.049245,0.030653],"unified_progress":[0.043247,0.086575,0.10216,0.10635,0.11333,0.10277,0.1012,0.088546,0.081743,0.069777,0.060535,0.043775]},{"section":9,"text":"Ciliated cells make me think of something called a serous cystadenoma because they're known for having these kinds of cells.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.030088,0.049376,0.066437,0.082854,0.098227,0.10781,0.11522,0.1121,0.11214,0.11179,0.077165,0.036796],"unified_progress":[0.037044,0.061179,0.081962,0.09609,0.10259,0.11623,0.10615,0.10121,0.092111,0.084984,0.068253,0.052203]},{"section":10,"text":"But hold on, let's not jump to conclusions too quickly.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.11289,0.090182,0.085014,0.077766,0.078845,0.08125,0.083509,0.091127,0.080785,0.054726,0.056411,0.10749],"unified_progress":[0.20455,0.077179,0.06502,0.065192,0.074358,0.073681,0.1065,0.081994,0.078529,0.062019,0.05726,0.053713]},{"section":11,"text":"There's another type of tumor that comes to mind - a mucinous cystadenoma.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.02581,0.045071,0.063467,0.079726,0.09033,0.10371,0.11372,0.1166,0.11999,0.12138,0.082245,0.037959],"unified_progress":[0.038271,0.067794,0.063447,0.099039,0.10617,0.10477,0.10355,0.10584,0.098718,0.091251,0.071453,0.049706]},{"section":12,"text":"They often have tall columnar epithelium too, but they usually have more mucus-producing cells.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.032992,0.041695,0.057453,0.073655,0.088311,0.10084,0.11077,0.11447,0.11896,0.12154,0.091832,0.047481],"unified_progress":[0.041768,0.058689,0.077009,0.089872,0.097913,0.10468,0.1028,0.10244,0.098837,0.093216,0.075264,0.05751]},{"section":13,"text":"Hmm, I'm not seeing anything about mucus here, so that makes me lean away from mucinous.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.019778,0.03564,0.050899,0.064269,0.077458,0.093879,0.10955,0.12599,0.13781,0.1337,0.099754,0.051275],"unified_progress":[0.031419,0.054182,0.070101,0.080048,0.091901,0.094189,0.099099,0.10517,0.10542,0.11252,0.091193,0.064751]},{"section":14,"text":"Also, the fact that she's only 23 years old is important.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.046456,0.057419,0.066288,0.075451,0.083067,0.091063,0.097778,0.10433,0.10942,0.11216,0.096041,0.060529],"unified_progress":[0.048415,0.067772,0.075409,0.082406,0.088756,0.091705,0.097074,0.097915,0.097677,0.098949,0.087017,0.066905]},{"section":15,"text":"Serous tumors tend to show up in younger women, especially when they're benign.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.03658,0.043132,0.055288,0.068333,0.080775,0.093129,0.10479,0.11015,0.11738,0.12464,0.10254,0.063268],"unified_progress":[0.041371,0.056241,0.075138,0.083304,0.09131,0.10232,0.10007,0.1009,0.097806,0.095463,0.08445,0.071625]},{"section":16,"text":"Mucinous ones are more common in older women, and they're often bigger and more complex.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.034544,0.040393,0.052532,0.065387,0.078638,0.092642,0.10576,0.11495,0.12431,0.12927,0.10283,0.058747],"unified_progress":[0.041423,0.05623,0.072812,0.083048,0.091712,0.098856,0.10025,0.10271,0.1007,0.10072,0.084995,0.066538]},{"section":17,"text":"So, putting all this together, the age, the size of the 